Welcome to download Tencent News APP and read more about the quality of its newsAPP. Facing the epidemic, we need the whole Chinese industry to work together to overcome this affliction. For the second installment, it is the second in a series of reports documenting China's Huaneng company, which helped build the Lei Shenshan Hospital.
要快，要更快。
Be quick, be faster.
天津姑娘方小玙接到了一项任务，把32.5吨方钢从天津运往武汉军运村，这些钢材是武汉雷神山医院ICU病区建设所需的方管。
After receiving the assignment, Ms. Fang got the 32.5 tons of steel from Tianjin to Wuhan Junyun Village. The steel was needed for the construction of the ICU at Wuhan Shen Shan Hospital.
1月23日，武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部宣布，将在武汉蔡甸和江夏两处同时开工，建设床位约1000个的火神山医院于2月2日交付投用；拟建床位约1500个的雷神山医院于2月5日交付投用。
On January 23, the Wuhan New Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command announced the start of construction of two new hospitals, Cai Jian and Jiangxia, in Wuhan. The hospital, with about 1,000 beds, was delivered on February 2 and the proposed 1,500-bed Lui Shenshan Hospital was delivered for operation on February 5.
中国华能旗下上海电商公司总经理胡俊和业务总监王飞，与火神山和雷神山供应链合作伙伴中建三局取得联系，沟通建设医院的物资需求。
Huaneng Shanghai Electric Company General Manager Hu Jun and business director Wang Fei, and Luo Shenshan and Lei Shenshan supply chain partners to establish contact between the three bureaus, to communicate the material needs of building hospitals.
获知雷神山医院ICU病房工程用方管的需求后，王飞在天津找到了一批方管。
After learning the demand of ICU ward of Lei Shenshan Hospital, Wang Fei found a batch of square pipes in Tianjin.
而运输的任务落到了华能旗下的华能真好运平台，这是一家物流行业的O2O公司。
And the task of transport fell to Huaneng Huaneng really good luck platform, which is a logistics industry O2O company.
方小玙是华能真好运公司天津的员工，重任落到了她的肩上。
Fang Xiaozheng is an employee of Huaneng Good Luck Company in Tianjin and the burden falls on her shoulders.
她感觉到了时间的紧迫性，对她来说，第一时间就是找车。
She felt the urgency of the time. For her, the first time was to find a car.
如果放在平常，找车非常简单。
It's easy to find a car if it's normal.
这是因为过去一周多时间，全国各地的物资正紧急运往武汉等湖北疫区，正值春节假期，大部分运输公司刚好处于“半歇业”状态，可以调动的运力资源本就有限，隔离政策加剧运力匮乏。
In the past week or so, supplies from all over the country have been transported to Wuhan and other epidemic areas in Hubei Province on an emergency basis. During the Spring Festival holiday, most of the transportation companies are in a state of "semi-shutdown," limited transportation resources can be mobilized, and the isolation policy exacerbates the shortage of capacity.
1月30日（大年初六）晚上十一点十四分，方小玙微信联系了8家过去合作过的物流公司，有三家电话可以打得通。
January 30 (about 6 pm) 11: 14 p.m., Fang Xiaoyu micro-letter contact 8 past cooperation logistics companies, there are three phone can work.
半个小时后，12点28分，有一家答应方小玙可以送货，她才觉得踏实了些。
After half an hour, at 12: 28, a promised little girl was able to deliver, and she felt relieved.
差不多同一时间节点，华能真好运的CEO曹猛给方小玙和财务总监拉了一个群。
About the same time node, Huaneng really good luck CEO Cao Meng gave Fang Xiaoxia and Financial Director pull a group.
曹猛告诉财务总监，请他协助付款的工作。
Cao Meng told the finance director to ask him to help pay for the work.
所有的准备工作都做完，已经凌晨两点多了。
All the preparations had been made, and it was past two in the morning.
方小玙发现老板到两点也没休息。
Fang found that the boss did not rest until two o'clock.
整个春节，曹猛在上海过了一个大年初一，就匆匆返回无锡了，因为真好运调车的团队在无锡。
The whole Spring Festival, Cao Meng in Shanghai after a New Year's Day, hurried back to Wuxi, because really good luck to transfer the team in Wuxi.
整个春节假期，到1月27日的时候，整个货运的需求量变得非常大。
Throughout the Spring Festival, by January 27, the overall demand for goods had become very large.
曹猛告诉《深网》，他一直找各种各样的运力，把到武汉的物资运送过去。
Cao Meng told Deep Net that he had been looking for all kinds of capacity to transport supplies to Wuhan.
把天津方钢运送到武汉，曹猛就全权委托给方小玙。
Tianjin Fanggang sent to Wuhan, Cao Meng on the full power to entrust Fang Xiaofu.
方小玙睡了四个小时，第二天早晨，财务总监第一时间把所有的文件都准备好了。
Fang slept for four hours. The next morning, the treasurer had all the papers ready.
万事俱备，只欠东风。
Everything is ready except the east wind.
方小玙在等车到达天津，结果车不来了。
Fang Xiao was waiting for the bus to arrive in Tianjin.
1月31日早晨六点多，方小玙得到信息，答应送货的那个司机反悔了，家里人不让他去。
After six o'clock in the morning of January 31, Fang got the information and the driver who promised to deliver the goods broke down.
方小玙很理解司机师傅，司机师傅从武汉回来要隔离14天。
Fang Xiaodi understood the master driver, who returned from Wuhan to be isolated for 14 days.
她继续跟另外几家物流公司联系，在6点38分的时候确定了承运车辆，河北籍师傅周志洪。
She went on to contact several other logistics companies and at 6: 38 identified the carrier, Hebei teacher Zhou Zhihong.
联系好车辆后，方小玙开始着手落实垫付款，因为财务总监已经确认好了付款手续。
After contacting the car, Fang began to implement the advance payment, because the finance director had confirmed the payment procedures.
8点20分，真好运员工刘建檀来到了天津静海区中兴储运院内，他从家打车过来花了50分钟。
At 8: 20, really lucky employee Liu Jiantan came to Tianjin Jinghai Zhongxing storage and transportation yard, he took 50 minutes to take a taxi from home.
今年31岁的刘建檀，30号晚上从老家刚刚开车回天津。
Liu Jiantan, 31, had just driven back to Tianjin from his hometown on the evening of the 30th.
刘建檀来到装货现场后，在仓库检验货物，与工厂联系人见面完成对接后，他开始准备装货文件、司机委托合同、代付货款委托书、装车明细等相关材料。
Liu Jiantan arrived at the loading site, in the warehouse inspection of the goods, meet with factory contacts to complete docking, he began to prepare loading documents, drivers commissioned contracts, payment orders, loading details and other related materials.
“爸爸去支援疫区了”货车司机是河北沧州东光人，叫周志洪，今年37岁，疫情施虐，整个春节周志洪都窝在家里，没有出门串门。
"Dad went to support the epidemic area" truck driver is Cangzhou Dongguang, Hebei Province, called Zhou Zhihong, 37 years old, the outbreak of abuse, the entire Spring Festival Zhou Zhihong nest at home, did not go out to visit.
周志洪开了十年的大货车，对他来说，从天津到武汉这1100公里不长，但雷神山医院的建设，是多么重要的事情。
Zhou Zhihong drove a 10-year-old truck, from Tianjin to Wuhan, this 1100 kilometers is not long, but the construction of Lei Shenshan Hospital, is how important things.
他答应接下这单货，同时，他在心理默默做了决定，为了不让家人担心，他不告诉家人他去那里。
He agreed to take the order and, at the same time, made a decision in silence that he would not tell his family where he was going so as not to worry his family.
虽然武汉是疫区，在周志洪看来，城里还有上千万人，不可能人人都染病，再说他过去也只是卸个货。
Although Wuhan is an epidemic area, in the view of Zhou Zhihong, there are tens of millions of people in the city, it is impossible for everyone to get sick, and he used to just unload goods.
一大早，天刚蒙蒙亮，周志洪从河北沧州出发前往天津，12点40分，他到了装货现场。
Early in the morning, just after dawn, Zhou Zhihong from Cangzhou, Hebei Province to Tianjin, 12: 40, he arrived at the loading site.
周志洪，刘建檀和库房两名工人师傅开始装车。
Zhou Zhihong, Liu Jiantan and the warehouse two workers began loading cars.
所有人都在争分夺秒。
Everyone's fighting for time.
“工人师傅指挥倒车的间隙，我和另一名师傅开始验货点数，因为成捆的方管有4根和3根两种，所以根据车辆载重和稳定性，做了一下装车计划，装车时一名工人师傅控制吊车另一名师傅记录磅数，我和司机师傅在车上挂钩、摘钩。
"When the master told me to reverse the car, I and another master began checking points because there were four and three bundles of square possession. So we made a loading plan according to the load and stability of the vehicle.
指挥吊车微调。
Command crane fine tuning.
”刘建檀向《深网》描述。
Liu Jiantan described it to Deep Web.
13点07分，全部货物装车完毕，刘建檀长舒了一口气，他看了看四周。
At 13: 07 all the goods were loaded, and with a sigh of relief, Liu Jianghuang looked around.
当天装货只有他们这一辆车，装货的过程中大家都带着口罩，装完货就匆匆回家了。
They were the only vehicle loading the day, loading the process of wearing masks, after loading goods hurried home.
14点07分，方小玙完成货款代付工作，根据发货清单制作货物签收单。
At 14: 07, Fang completed the payment on behalf of the work, according to the delivery list to produce goods signed receipt.
15点，周志洪带好所有文件自提货地出发，驶向京台高速。
At 15 o'clock, Zhou Zhihong took all the documents from the pick-up point to the Beijing-Taiwan Expressway.
他设计的线路是京台高速-大广高速-沪蓉高速-目的地，总共1100公里。
The route he designed was the Beijing-Tai Expressway-Shanghai-Rong high-speed-destination, a total of 1,100 kilometers.
他准备好了防护服，口罩和手套。
He's got his suit, mask and gloves.
在中国，像周志洪这样的卡车司机太多了，他们在公路上穿梭，承担了70%以上的货运量。
In China, there are too many truckers like Zhou Zhihong, who travel the highways and carry more than 70% of the freight.
道路绵延和起伏，开了10个小时后，已是凌晨。
It was early morning, after ten hours of rolling and rolling roads.
或许是因为正月的缘故，路面上车并不多，路况也算良好，但周志洪很困了。
Perhaps because of the first month, the road is not many, the road conditions are also good, but Zhou Zhihong very sleepy.
大货车行驶到山东菏泽曹县服务站的时候，周志洪休息了一次，加油吃饭稍作休整，停留了4个多小时，本想睡一觉再出发，但是他路上接到了通知，这批货非常急，必须赶在2月1号下午到。
Zhou Zhihong took a rest when he drove to the service station of Heze County in Shandong Province. He stopped for more than four hours for a short rest and wanted to get some sleep before starting.
货车驶出沪蓉高速，驶入武汉境内时，他看到了身穿防护服的检查员，他心里生出了一丝紧张和不安，但这种不安很快就消解了。
As the lorry pulled out of Wuhan, he saw the inspector in protective clothing. There was a tinge of nervousness in his mind, but it soon dissipated.
2月1日下午1点，周志洪的车到了武汉军运村，19个小时他开了1100公里，他整个人放松了下来，他觉得他完成了一项任务。
On February 1 at 1: 00 p.m., Zhou Zhihong's car arrived at Wuhan military transport village, 19 hours he drove 1100 kilometers, he relaxed, he felt that he completed a task.
周志洪开了十年的大货车，他觉得以往都是在送货，但这次送钢材不同。
Zhou Zhihong drove a ten-year-old truck, which he thought used to be delivering goods, but this time the steel was different.
他觉得到家了就可以告诉家人，他去了武汉，告诉孩子，“爸爸去支援疫区去了，不是去跑长途了。
He felt he could tell his family when he got home. He went to Wuhan and told the child, "Dad has gone to support the epidemic area.
”雷神山医院所需的32.5吨钢材，仅仅19个小时，就从天津静海区运到了武汉军运村，这仅仅是雷神山医院建设中一个争分夺秒的小细节。
The 32.5 tons of steel needed by Raytheon Mountain Hospital, transported just 19 hours from Tianjin Jinghai to Wuhan's Junyun Village, is just a small, time-consuming detail in the construction of Lui Shenshan Hospital.
而若干的小细节的汇聚在一起，就足以解释为什么十天能建成一所医院。
The confluence of small details is enough to explain why a hospital can be built in ten days.
十天建成一所医院2月3日，火神山医院已经交付。
Ten days to complete a hospital Feb. 3, the fire god mountain hospital has been delivered.
雷神山医院的建设进展如何？2月2日，武汉雷神山医院项目总体进度完成65%。
How is the construction of Lei Shenshan Hospital progressing Feb. 2, the overall progress of the Wuhan Shen Shan Hospital project completed 65%.
隔离区完成60%，3300间集装箱，已到场2530间；土建部分完成约60%；隔离病房场地平整、沟槽开挖、沟槽管线预埋、沟槽回填、主管道面层浇筑、非沟槽区PE膜施工已全部完成。
The area of separation was completed with 60 per cent of the 3,300 containers on site; the civil construction component was approximately 60 per cent complete; the isolation ward site formation, trench excavation, trench line pre-burial, trench backfilling, executive road surface pouring, PE film construction in non-trench areas have all been completed.
距离武汉市中心20公里的西南角，已经是一个巨大的工地，机器的轰鸣声，焊接声，平安安静的黄家湖大道上，各种车辆、运送着货物，在马路上来回穿梭，还有正在工地上忙碌的工人们。
The southwest corner, 20 kilometers from the center of Wuhan, is already a huge construction site, with the roar of machines, the sound of welding, the peaceful and quiet Huangjia Lake Boulevard, vehicles, goods, shuttling back and forth on the road, and the busy workers at the construction site.
央视正在云直播着这场全国人们都关注的建筑工程——雷神山医院建设现场。
CCTV is broadcasting live the nationwide attention of the construction project - Lei Shenshan Hospital construction site.
透过24小时在线直播镜头，世界亿万人注视着医院建设的每一秒。
Millions of people around the world are watching every second of hospital construction through 24-hour live streaming.
中建三局是雷神山医院的承建方，中建三局第一建设工程有限责任公司山东公司副总经理朱国升在接受采访时表示，接到命令后，中建三局一公司华南公司支援120套厢式板房，用30余辆35吨位的货运车连夜运往武汉。
CCB III was the party under construction at Lui Shenshan Hospital. In an interview, Zhu Guosheng, Vice General Manager of Shandong Company of China Construction Engineering Co. Ltd., was ordered to provide support for 120 sets of cartons with more than 30 35-tonne cargo trucks overnight to Wuhan.
华东公司连夜运送集装箱510个、走道箱100个；西部公司承担210套标准箱、200套走道箱施工任务；北方公司支援1134套厢式板房……这些物资包括汽车吊平板车、叉车、登高车、发电机等基础建设工具，也包括塑料管、洁具、配电箱、分体空调、紫外线杀菌灯、电加热灭菌机组等安装组件。
East China Company transports 510 containers and 100 walkways overnight; Western Company supports 210 sets of standard containers and 200 walkway boxes; Northern Company supports 1,134 containers... including plastic hoists, forklifts, elevators, generators, and other installation components such as plastic pipes, fixtures, distribution boxes, split air conditioners, ultraviolet sterilizers, electric heating sterilization units, etc.
与此同时，承建方中建三局全国施从工人员到管理人员，也整装向武汉出发。
At the same time, it was built three bureaus throughout the country, from workers to managers, and set out for Wuhan.
朱国升介绍，在武汉施工现场，工程系统安排井井有条，不同的公司根据自身的特点进行相应施工，分别处理基建、医疗隔离区、医疗污水处理、室内设计、排水等。
Zhu Guosheng introduced that in Wuhan construction site, the engineering system is well organized, different companies according to their own characteristics to carry out the corresponding construction, respectively dealing with infrastructure, medical isolation zone, medical sewage treatment, interior design, drainage, etc.
“我们统一指挥、分工建设、同时制造，才能保证速度。
"We can guarantee speed by unified command, division of labor and manufacturing.
”朱国升所在的中建三局一公司山东公司负责搭建火神山医院的5000平米板房和为雷神山医院建设供应1134套箱式板房。
Zhu Guosheng's three bureaus, a Shandong company, are responsible for building 5,000 square meters of board rooms at the Mount Huoshen Hospital and 1134 units of box-type rooms for the construction of Lui Shenshan Hospital.
通过内部系统工程优化，工期大大缩短，速度得到保障。
Through the optimization of internal system engineering, the construction period is greatly shortened and the speed is guaranteed.
“施工现场，建设团队不分昼夜，歇人不歇工，中建三局的员工大多来源于湖北，大家都憋着一股劲，必须以‘中国速度’跑赢疫情。
"The construction site, construction team day and night, rest people do not close, the staff of the construction of the three innings are mostly from Hubei, we are all suffocating to win the epidemic with 'Chinese speed'.
”朱国升接受采访时表示。
Zhu said in an interview.
此外，全国各地的物资也都在向武汉汇聚。
In addition, supplies from all over the country are converging to Wuhan.
5000平米板房、2134套箱式板房、1500多吨板材、31.43吨高质量彩涂板，32.5吨方钢……这些建筑部件和物资，争分夺秒，源源不断从全国各地运抵武汉火神山、雷神山医院。
Five thousand square meters slabs, 2,134 boxes of slab rooms, more than 1,500 tons of sheet metal, 31.43 tons of high-quality painted panels, 32.5 tons of square steel... these building parts and materials, from all over the country, continuously arrived at Wuhan Huoshen Mountain, Lei Shenshan Hospital.
现如今，火神山医院已经建成，雷神山医院的建成指日可待。
Now, the fire god mountain hospital has been completed, the construction of Lui Shenshan hospital is within sight.
